"data: {"choices":[{"delta":{"content":"# Average Speed Calculation\\n\\n## Step 1: Find the distance for each segment\\n\\n**First segment:**\\n- Speed = 60 mph, Time = 2 hours\\n- Distance = Speed × Time = 60 × 2 = **120 miles**\\n\\n**Second segment:**\\n- Speed = 80 mph, Time = 1 hour\\n- Distance = Speed × Time = 80 × 1 = **80 miles**\\n\\n## Step 2: Find total distance and total time\\n\\n- **Total distance** = 120 + 80 = **200 miles**\\n- **Total time** = 2 + 1 = **3 hours**\\n\\n## Step 3: Calculate average speed\\n\\n$$\\\\text{Average Speed} = \\\\frac{\\\\text{Total Distance}}{\\\\text{Total Time}} = \\\\frac{200}{3} = \\\\boxed{66.67 \\\\text{ mph}}$$\\n\\n**The average speed is approximately 66.67 mph** (or 66⅔ mph)","role":"assistant"},"finish_reason":"stop","index":0}],"id":"msg_vrtx_019F1t95kVe8RrfswTc8EgNE","model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","object":"chat.completion.chunk","usage":{"completion_tokens":235,"prompt_tokens":45,"prompt_tokens_details":{"cached_tokens":0},"total_tokens":280}}

